The <b><i>Map Layers</i></b> window uses a "tree" style menu.  Click the plus sign next to any category for an expanded view of layer symbology and available metadata.  In order to quickly view detailed symbology information for all available layers, click the <i>Expand All</i> button.  When finished, click <i>Collapse All</i> to return to the default Map Layers window.
